description: Welcome to a rare, fully renovated single family on South Boston's West Side! The home consists of three levels of living space and has been thoughtfully renovated throughout. The first floor features an inviting living room and a spacious eat in kitchen featuring all new cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The second floor features the master bedroom with a large ensuite and a generous second bedroom. The third floor features a roomy third bedroom that also has an ensuite bathroom and an additional large room that can be used as an office space or a fourth bedroom! The basement contains plenty of storage space and laundry machines. Enjoy a huge private deck located off the back of the house! This fully turn-key, stunning home sits in an incredible location in South Boston, just off of West Broadway! Close to the T Stop and all the best restaurants, bars, and shopping that the Southie lifestyle offers. Welcome to your new home!
